<Content>dont stay here or Pension baha or las ramblas i was sent here after their sister hotel Pension Bahia said they had no trace of my internet booking (i showed them the confirmation number + print out) conveniently she could no longer speak english.took me 1 hour to find the dingy picasso. woman here equally unfriendly and said didnt speak english or spanish and claimed to be french. i spoke french to her and she pretended not to understand.room like a prison cellno breakfast as was advertised on my original bookingno sleep what so ever noise mainly from outside. but some inside1 shower for seemingly every onedrugged out african prostitues hasseling me and even folowing me at night all bars and cafes overpriced and very poor quality.las ramblas is overated. only a few streets away the prices come down and quality gets better. no way would locals pay 5.50 euros for a beer and 7.50 for a sandwhich and small coffee.everything you want to see in barcelona is not on las ramblas anyway so do yourself a favour and get a proper hotel elsewhere it will be better value in the long run. 
